    "pages": [{"date":"2026-03-13","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/260313_fran-lebowitz_good-habits-wont-save/","summary":"Bad habits can kill you. I have seen that. But your good habits won\u0026rsquo;t save you.","tags":[],"text":"bad habits can kill you. i have seen that. but your good habits won\u0026rsquo;t save you.\n","title":""},{"date":"2025-12-15","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/251215_david-oreilly_art-for-not-being/","summary":"Basically art can allow us to feel less alone in the universe. Now life and other people often given us the opposite message. We like to emphasize our differences. I\u0026rsquo;m me and you are you and however unconsciously we can make each other feel more alone. So art is this way of teaching each other about the things we cant talk about. Its the most non-invasive way we have of touching each others brains.","tags":[],"text":"basically art can allow us to feel less alone in the universe. now life and other people often given us the opposite message. we like to emphasize our differences. i\u0026rsquo;m me and you are you and however unconsciously we can make each other feel more alone. so art is this way of teaching each other about the things we cant talk about. its the most non-invasive way we have of touching each others brains.\n","title":""},{"date":"2024-09-22","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/240922_nam-june-paik_use-tech-to-hate/","summary":"I use technology in order to hate it more properly.","tags":[],"text":"i use technology in order to hate it more properly.\n","title":""},{"date":"2023-08-10","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/230810_buckminster-fuller_buckminster-fuller/","summary":"Don’t destroy old systems, just make better ones.","tags":[],"text":"don’t destroy old systems, just make better ones.\n","title":""},{"date":"2022-07-16","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/220716_tolstoi_happy-families/","summary":"Happy families are all alike; every unhappy family is unhappy in its own way","tags":[],"text":"happy families are all alike; every unhappy family is unhappy in its own way\n","title":""},{"date":"2019-12-10","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/191210_fleabag_love-well-so-it/","summary":"I think you know how to love better than any of us. Thats why you find it all so painful.","tags":[],"text":"i think you know how to love better than any of us. thats why you find it all so painful.\n","title":""},{"date":"2019-07-28","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/190728_c%C3%A9sar-astudillo_no-juegues-con-el/","summary":"No juegues a ningún tipo de juego con el deseo. No juegues a dar celos, a fingir desinterés, o a erosionar la autoestima de la persona que te mola. Jugar a a esos juegos selecciona a la gente a la que les gusta jugar a esos juegos, y eso (en mi opinión) es en el peor de los casos el principio de algo chungo, y en el mejor, una pérdida de tiempo.","tags":[],"text":"no juegues a ningún tipo de juego con el deseo. no juegues a dar celos, a fingir desinterés, o a erosionar la autoestima de la persona que te mola. jugar a a esos juegos selecciona a la gente a la que les gusta jugar a esos juegos, y eso (en mi opinión) es en el peor de los casos el principio de algo chungo, y en el mejor, una pérdida de tiempo.\n","title":""},{"date":"2014-08-26","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/140826_butters_butters-south-park/","summary":"Son of a biscuit","tags":[],"text":"son of a biscuit\n","title":""},{"date":"2026-03-13","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/260313_philip-k.dick_jesucristo-maneja-ascensor/","summary":"Pero teníamos que subir en ascensor y desarrollé una fobia. Estaba bastante borracho cuando me vino la fobia, pero según lo que yo recuerdo y lo que me contaron otros, parece que yo no quería entrar en el ascensor porque el cable lo manejaba Jesucristo y nunca dejaríamos de subir.","tags":[],"text":"pero teníamos que subir en ascensor y desarrollé una fobia. estaba bastante borracho cuando me vino la fobia, pero según lo que yo recuerdo y lo que me contaron otros, parece que yo no quería entrar en el ascensor porque el cable lo manejaba jesucristo y nunca dejaríamos de subir.\n","title":""},{"date":"2025-01-22","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/250122_adam_stranger-in-my-own/","summary":"I always felt like a stranger in my own family. And then, coming out just puts a name to that difference thats always been there.","tags":[],"text":"i always felt like a stranger in my own family. and then, coming out just puts a name to that difference thats always been there.\n","title":""},{"date":"2022-07-03","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/220703_garry-nolan_speculation-creativity-beginning-hypothesis/","summary":"Speculation is just creativity. Speculation is the beginning of hypothesis.","tags":[],"text":"speculation is just creativity. speculation is the beginning of hypothesis.\n","title":""},{"date":"2021-06-28","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/210628_nick-cave_words-on-getting-old/","summary":"[About turning 40. What is your perspective on getting old?] REMKO, LANAKEN, BELGIUM\nDear Remko,\nMy advice to you is to grow a porn star moustache and learn the electric guitar — it worked for me — and try to hang in there until you’re sixty. Then you’ll find you don’t have to worry about what people say any more and, as a consequence, life becomes a whole lot more interesting.\nEntering your sixties brings with it a warm and fuzzy feeling of freedom through redundancy, through obsolescence, through living outside of the conversation and forever existing on the wrong end of the stick. What a relief it is to be that mad, embarrassing uncle in the corner of the room, a product of his age, with his loopy ideas about free speech and freedom of expression, with his love of beauty, of humour, chaos, provocation and outrage, of conversation and debate, his adoration of art without dogma, his impatience with the morally obvious, his belief in universal compassion, forgiveness and mercy, in nuance and the shadows, in neutrality and in humanity — ah, beautiful humanity — and in God too, who he thanks for letting him, in these dementing times, be old.\nLove Nick","tags":[],"text":"[about turning 40. what is your perspective on getting old?] remko, lanaken, belgium\ndear remko,\nmy advice to you is to grow a porn star moustache and learn the electric guitar — it worked for me — and try to hang in there until you’re sixty. then you’ll find you don’t have to worry about what people say any more and, as a consequence, life becomes a whole lot more interesting.\nentering your sixties brings with it a warm and fuzzy feeling of freedom through redundancy, through obsolescence, through living outside of the conversation and forever existing on the wrong end of the stick. what a relief it is to be that mad, embarrassing uncle in the corner of the room, a product of his age, with his loopy ideas about free speech and freedom of expression, with his love of beauty, of humour, chaos, provocation and outrage, of conversation and debate, his adoration of art without dogma, his impatience with the morally obvious, his belief in universal compassion, forgiveness and mercy, in nuance and the shadows, in neutrality and in humanity — ah, beautiful humanity — and in god too, who he thanks for letting him, in these dementing times, be old.\nlove nick\n","title":""},{"date":"2021-05-23","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/210523_david-sedaris_perdedor-o-marginal/","summary":"La persona que quería ganar sin conseguirlo era un perdedor, mientras que aquel a quien no le importaba era solo un marginal.","tags":[],"text":"la persona que quería ganar sin conseguirlo era un perdedor, mientras que aquel a quien no le importaba era solo un marginal.\n","title":""},{"date":"2021-05-23","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/210523_kassa-overall_meaning-of-algorithms/","summary":"What’s meaning of algorithms if the rhythm is out of rhythm I could give them that power-pivot I was living without a gimmick now they want it I gotta give it.","tags":[],"text":"what’s meaning of algorithms if the rhythm is out of rhythm i could give them that power-pivot i was living without a gimmick now they want it i gotta give it.\n","title":""},{"date":"2020-07-01","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/200701_blaise-pascal_cannot-sit-alone-quietly/","summary":"All of humanity’s problems stem from man’s inability to sit quietly in a room alone.","tags":[],"text":"all of humanity’s problems stem from man’s inability to sit quietly in a room alone.\n","title":""},{"date":"2019-02-27","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/190227_arthur-schopenhauer_talento-y-genio-apuntan/","summary":"El talento se asemeja a un tirador que hace diana en un objetivo que los demás no pueden alcanzar; el genio alcanza un objetivo que los demás no pueden ver.","tags":[],"text":"el talento se asemeja a un tirador que hace diana en un objetivo que los demás no pueden alcanzar; el genio alcanza un objetivo que los demás no pueden ver.\n","title":""},{"date":"2014-02-03","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/140203_magritte_piensa-menudo-muerte-menos/","summary":"-Piensa a menudo en la muerte?\n-No, no con menos frecuencia que en la vida.","tags":[],"text":"-piensa a menudo en la muerte?\n-no, no con menos frecuencia que en la vida.\n","title":""},{"date":"2026-03-13","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/260313_fran-lebowitz_read-before-you-think/","summary":"Think before you speak. Read before you think.","tags":[],"text":"think before you speak. read before you think.\n","title":""},{"date":"2026-03-13","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/260313_tom-waits_historias-destr%C3%A1s-de-las/","summary":"Es una canción - dijo-, y las historias que hay detrás de la mayoría de las canciones son menos interesantes que las canciones en sí.","tags":[],"text":"es una canción - dijo-, y las historias que hay detrás de la mayoría de las canciones son menos interesantes que las canciones en sí.\n","title":""},{"date":"2024-04-12","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/240412_jaron-lanier_sigue-el-dinero-y/","summary":"Si te interesa saber lo que sucede realmente en una sociedad o ideología, solo tienes que seguir la ruta del dinero. Si va a parar a la publicidad y no a los músicos, los periodistas y los artistas, entonces esa sociedad está más interesada en la manipulación que en la verdad o la belleza. Sin el contenido carece de valor, entonces la gente empezará a volverse tonta e insustancial.","tags":[],"text":"si te interesa saber lo que sucede realmente en una sociedad o ideología, solo tienes que seguir la ruta del dinero. si va a parar a la publicidad y no a los músicos, los periodistas y los artistas, entonces esa sociedad está más interesada en la manipulación que en la verdad o la belleza. sin el contenido carece de valor, entonces la gente empezará a volverse tonta e insustancial.\n","title":""},{"date":"2022-05-23","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/220523_vangelis_invest-in-beauty/","summary":"What we need today more than anything else is to invest in beauty, because beauty is harmony which comes from chaos. But we invest in chaos, because chaos is much more profitable than peace\u0026hellip; Beauty is a kind of safety vault for people.","tags":[],"text":"what we need today more than anything else is to invest in beauty, because beauty is harmony which comes from chaos. but we invest in chaos, because chaos is much more profitable than peace\u0026hellip; beauty is a kind of safety vault for people.\n","title":""},{"date":"2021-08-22","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/210822_mcluhan_shape-tools-us/","summary":"We shape our tools and then our tools shape us.","tags":[],"text":"we shape our tools and then our tools shape us.\n","title":""},{"date":"2020-11-01","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/201101_john-allen-paulos_los-g%C3%A9minis-no-creen/","summary":"\u0026ldquo;Cuando le preguntan por qué no cree en la astrología, el lógico Raymond Smullyan contesta que es Géminis y los Géminis no creen en la astrología\u0026rdquo;","tags":[],"text":"\u0026ldquo;cuando le preguntan por qué no cree en la astrología, el lógico raymond smullyan contesta que es géminis y los géminis no creen en la astrología\u0026rdquo;\n","title":""},{"date":"2018-10-27","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/181027_trevor-paglen_need-think-about-time/","summary":"We need to think about time differently, so that the future does not become the enemy of the present.","tags":[],"text":"we need to think about time differently, so that the future does not become the enemy of the present.\n","title":""},{"date":"2013-10-27","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/131027_samuel-beckett_words-stain-silence-and/","summary":"Cada palabra es una mancha innecesaria en el silencio y la nada.","tags":[],"text":"cada palabra es una mancha innecesaria en el silencio y la nada.\n","title":""},{"date":"2025-06-08","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/250608_wes-anderson_writing-is-excavation/","summary":"When you are writing a story, it often feels less like you are doing architecture and more like you are doing excavation, like it\u0026rsquo;s something that already exists and we are just unearthing it and you know it\u0026r