n ninguna de ellas, nadie pueda reprocharnos nada.\n","title":""},{"date":"2014-06-29","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/140629_cartman_im-half-bisexual/","summary":"So, I\u0026rsquo;m half bisexual","tags":[],"text":"so, i\u0026rsquo;m half bisexual\n","title":""},{"date":"2013-10-03","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/131003_albert-einstein_expl%C3%ADcalo-a-tu-abuela/","summary":"No entiendes realmente algo a menos que seas capaz de explicárselo a tu abuela.","tags":[],"text":"no entiendes realmente algo a menos que seas capaz de explicárselo a tu abuela.\n","title":""},{"date":"2025-12-24","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/251224_milan-kundera_memoria-contra-olvido/","summary":"La lucha del hombre contra el poder es la lucha de la memoria contra el olvido.","tags":[],"text":"la lucha del hombre contra el poder es la lucha de la memoria contra el olvido.\n","title":""},{"date":"2025-12-15","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/251215_daniel-ausente_otorrinolaring%C3%B3logo-al-rev%C3%A9s/","summary":"Mi tío me enseñó a decir otorrinolaringólogo al revés y hoy es lo mejor que sé hacer en la vida.","tags":[],"text":"mi tío me enseñó a decir otorrinolaringólogo al revés y hoy es lo mejor que sé hacer en la vida.\n","title":""},{"date":"2024-07-04","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/240704_blixa-bargeld_blixa-bargeld/","summary":"I did not join a rock and roll band to play rock and roll!","tags":[],"text":"i did not join a rock and roll band to play rock and roll!\n","title":""},{"date":"2024-04-12","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/240412_alberti_movimientos-del-alma/","summary":"Los movimientos del alma se conocen por los movimientos del cuerpo.","tags":[],"text":"los movimientos del alma se conocen por los movimientos del cuerpo.\n","title":""},{"date":"2024-04-12","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/240412_bill-murray_sign-language-while-driving/","summary":"¿Se debería permitir que las personas sordomudas hablen con las manos mientras conducen?","tags":[],"text":"¿se debería permitir que las personas sordomudas hablen con las manos mientras conducen?\n","title":""},{"date":"2023-11-17","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/231117_karl-ove-knausgard_childs-are-within-the/","summary":"What makes life worth living? No child asks itself that question. To children life is self-evident. Life goes without saying: whether it is good or bad makes no difference. This is because children don\u0026rsquo;t see the world, don\u0026rsquo;t observe the world, don\u0026rsquo;t contemplate the world, but are so deeply immersed in the world that they don\u0026rsquo;t distinguish between it and their own selves.","tags":[],"text":"what makes life worth living? no child asks itself that question. to children life is self-evident. life goes without saying: whether it is good or bad makes no difference. this is because children don\u0026rsquo;t see the world, don\u0026rsquo;t observe the world, don\u0026rsquo;t contemplate the world, but are so deeply immersed in the world that they don\u0026rsquo;t distinguish between it and their own selves.\n","title":""},{"date":"2021-12-14","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/211214_li-po_the-mountain-and-i/","summary":"We have never grown tired of each other, the mountain and I.","tags":[],"text":"we have never grown tired of each other, the mountain and i.\n","title":""},{"date":"2021-07-10","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/210710_arthur-c.-clarke_vida-inteligente/","summary":"O bien hay vida inteligente en el universo, o bien no la hay. Cualquiera de las dos cosas es aterradora.","tags":[],"text":"o bien hay vida inteligente en el universo, o bien no la hay. cualquiera de las dos cosas es aterradora.\n","title":""},{"date":"2019-06-09","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/190609_francisco-goya_el-sabio-desconf%C3%ADa/","summary":"En todas ciencias hay charlatanes que sin haber estudiado palabra lo saben todo y para todo hayan remedio. No hay que fiarse de lo que anuncian. El verdadero sabio, desconfía siempre del acierto, promete poco y cumple mucho.","tags":[],"text":"en todas ciencias hay charlatanes que sin haber estudiado palabra lo saben todo y para todo hayan remedio. no hay que fiarse de lo que anuncian. el verdadero sabio, desconfía siempre del acierto, promete poco y cumple mucho.\n","title":""},{"date":"2018-10-14","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/181014_kino_el-mundo-no-es/","summary":"El mundo no es hermoso, por tanto lo es.","tags":[],"text":"el mundo no es hermoso, por tanto lo es.\n","title":""},{"date":"2015-12-16","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/151216_linda-belcher_linda-belcher-bobs-burger/","summary":"You got the moves, but there is no fire","tags":[],"text":"you got the moves, but there is no fire\n","title":""},{"date":"2015-03-12","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/150312_joan-didion_escribo-saber-qu%C3%A9-estoy/","summary":"Yo solo escribo para saber qué estoy pensando, qué estoy viendo y qué significa\u0026hellip;","tags":[],"text":"yo solo escribo para saber qué estoy pensando, qué estoy viendo y qué significa\u0026hellip;\n","title":""},{"date":"2026-03-13","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/260313_ray-bradbury_arte-y-ciencia-y/","summary":"Combinaron [los marcianos] religión, arte y ciencia, pues en verdad la ciencia no es más que la investigación de un milagro inexplicable, y el arte, la interpretación de ese milagro. No permitieron que la ciencia aplastara la belleza. Se trata simplemente de una cuestión de grados. Un hombre de la Tierra piensa: “En ese cuadro no hay realmente color. Un físico puede probar que elcolor es sólo una forma de la materia, un reflejo de la luz, no la realidad misma”. Un marciano, mucho más inteligente, diría: “Este cuadro es hermoso. Nació de la mano y la mente de un hombre inspirado. El tema y los colores vienen de la vida. Es una cosa buena”.","tags":[],"text":"combinaron [los marcianos] religión, arte y ciencia, pues en verdad la ciencia no es más que la investigación de un milagro inexplicable, y el arte, la interpretación de ese milagro. no permitieron que la ciencia aplastara la belleza. se trata simplemente de una cuestión de grados. un hombre de la tierra piensa: “en ese cuadro no hay realmente color. un físico puede probar que elcolor es sólo una forma de la materia, un reflejo de la luz, no la realidad misma”. un marciano, mucho más inteligente, diría: “este cuadro es hermoso. nació de la mano y la mente de un hombre inspirado. el tema y los colores vienen de la vida. es una cosa buena”.\n","title":""},{"date":"2026-03-08","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/260308_irene-men%C3%A9ndez-hastings_no-pienses-tanto/","summary":"No piense más, va a tener cien mil pasados y ningún futuro.","tags":[],"text":"no piense más, va a tener cien mil pasados y ningún futuro.\n","title":""},{"date":"2025-05-27","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/250527_dem%C3%B3crito_el-sabio-tiene-tierras/","summary":"Todas las tierras están abiertas al sabio, pues la patria de un alma virtuosa es el universo.","tags":[],"text":"todas las tierras están abiertas al sabio, pues la patria de un alma virtuosa es el universo.\n","title":""},{"date":"2025-01-04","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/250104_chris-marker_nothing-left-to-invent/","summary":"When all one\u0026rsquo;s energy is required to stay afloat, there is hardly anything left to invent the future.","tags":[],"text":"when all one\u0026rsquo;s energy is required to stay afloat, there is hardly anything left to invent the future.\n","title":""},{"date":"2024-03-13","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/240313_david-byrne_i-am-what-i/","summary":"Unfortunately, I am what I am.","tags":[],"text":"unfortunately, i am what i am.\n","title":""},{"date":"2022-11-29","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/221129_richard-feynman_knowledge-right-answers-intelligence/","summary":"Knowledge is having the right answers. Intelligence is asking the right questions. Wisdom is knowing when to ask the right questions.","tags":[],"text":"knowledge is having the right answers. intelligence is asking the right questions. wisdom is knowing when to ask the right questions.\n","title":""},{"date":"2020-12-17","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/201217_matt-furie_cartoons-are-powerfull/","summary":"\u0026ldquo;Whats more worthless than cartoons?\u0026rdquo; But like, \u0026ldquo;Whats more powerful than Mickey Mouse?\u0026rdquo;","tags":[],"text":"\u0026ldquo;whats more worthless than cartoons?\u0026rdquo; but like, \u0026ldquo;whats more powerful than mickey mouse?\u0026rdquo;\n","title":""},{"date":"2020-11-07","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/201107_alan-kay_inventa-el-futuro/","summary":"La mejor forma de predecir el futuro es inventarlo.","tags":[],"text":"la mejor forma de predecir el futuro es inventarlo.\n","title":""},{"date":"2018-01-07","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/180107_hobbes_preveer-consecuencias/","summary":"No hay nada que dirija tan bien a los hombres en sus deliberaciones como la previsión de las consecuencias de sus acciones; la profecía es muchas veces la causa principal de los acontecimientos pronosticados.","tags":[],"text":"no hay nada que dirija tan bien a los hombres en sus deliberaciones como la previsión de las consecuencias de sus acciones; la profecía es muchas veces la causa principal de los acontecimientos pronosticados.\n","title":""},{"date":"2014-11-09","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/141109_%C3%A1ngel_sangre-de-tu-sangre/","summary":"Vigila ese tono, que sea sangre de tu sangre no significa que no te la haga escupir.","tags":[],"text":"vigila ese tono, que sea sangre de tu sangre no significa que no te la haga escupir.\n","title":""},{"date":"2026-03-13","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/260313_leonardo-da-vinci_hombre-imagen-mundo/","summary":"El hombre es la imagen del mundo.","tags":[],"text":"el hombre es la imagen del mundo.\n","title":""},{"date":"2026-03-13","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/260313_ray-bradbury_observando-todo/","summary":"Papá se pasaba el tiempo escuchando o canturreando u observando todas las cosas, atándose a ellas como si el mundo fuese una máquina centrífuga que pudiera arrojarlo, en cualquier momento, muy lejos de nosotros.","tags":[],"text":"papá se pasaba el tiempo escuchando o canturreando u observando todas las cosas, atándose a ellas como si el mundo fuese una máquina centrífuga que pudiera arrojarlo, en cualquier momento, muy lejos de nosotros.\n","title":""},{"date":"2024-06-08","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/240608_lain_serial-experiments-lain/","summary":"Nunca sucedió si no hay recuerdos de ello. La memoria humana es solo un registro. Sólo necesitas reescribir ese registro.","tags":[],"text":"nunca sucedió si no hay recuerdos de ello. la memoria humana es solo un registro. sólo necesitas reescribir ese registro.\n","title":""},{"date":"2022-02-02","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/220202_jason-fried_when-someone-copies-theyre/","summary":"When someone copies you, they\u0026rsquo;re copying a moment in time. They don’t know the thinking that went into getting you to that moment in time, and they won’t know the thinking that’ll help you have a million more moments in time. They’re stuck with what you left behind.","tags":[],"text":"when someone copies you, they\u0026rsquo;re copying a moment in time. they don’t know the thinking that went into getting you to that moment in time, and they won’t know the thinking that’ll help you have a million more moments in time. they’re stuck with what you left behind.\n","title":""},{"date":"2021-06-14","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/210614_shirley_vigors-youth-wasted-young/","summary":"Vigors of youth, wasted on the young.","tags":[],"text":"vigors of youth, wasted on the young.\n","title":""},{"date":"2021-05-23","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/210523_warren-ellis_warren-ellis-spider-jerusalem/","summary":"Los paranoicos sólo son personas con todos los hechos","tags":[],"text":"los paranoicos sólo son personas con todos los hechos\n","title":""},{"date":"2020-09-26","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/200926_bren%C3%A9-brown_bren%C3%A9-brown/","summary":"We live in a vulnerable world. The problem is that you cannot selectively numb emotions. You can\u0026rsquo;t say, here\u0026rsquo;s the bad stuff. Here is vulnerability, here is grief, here is shame, here is fear, here is disappointment. I don\u0026rsquo;t want to feel these. I\u0026rsquo;m going to have a couple of beers and a banana nut muffin. [\u0026hellip;] You can\u0026rsquo;t numb those hard feelings without numbing the other affects, our emotions. You cannot selectively numb. So when we numb those, we numb joy, we numb gratitude, we numb happiness. And then, we are miserable, and we looking for purpose and meaning.","tags":[],"text":"we live in a vulnerable world. the problem is that you cannot selectively numb emotions. you can\u0026rsquo;t say, here\u0026rsquo;s the bad stuff. here is vulnerability, here is grief, here is shame, here is fear, here is disappointment. i don\u0026rsquo;t want to feel these. i\u0026rsquo;m going to have a couple of beers and a banana nut muffin. [\u0026hellip;] you can\u0026rsquo;t numb those hard feelings without numbing the other affects, our emotions. you cannot selectively numb. so when we numb those, we numb joy, we numb gratitude, we numb happiness. and then, we are miserable, and we looking for purpose and meaning.\n","title":""},{"date":"2025-04-15","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/250415_alok_therapy-for-better-describe/","summary":"I just have some questions for those of you in therapy. Whats the point in healing. Now I just have a more expansive vocabulary to describe how fucked up I am, but I still feel fucked up.","tags":[],"text":"i just have some questions for those of you in therapy. whats the point in healing. now i just have a more expansive vocabulary to describe how fucked up i am, but i still feel fucked up.\n","title":""},{"date":"2023-08-10","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/230810_donald-knuth_premature-optimization/","summary":"Premature optimization is the root of all evil.","tags":[],"text":"premature optimization is the root of all evil.\n","title":""},{"date":"2023-07-23","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/230723_jaime-altozano_defectos-antiguo-nostalgia-futuro/","summary":"Los defectos de lo antiguo son la nostalgia del futuro. (hablando de los errores en IA. Por ej, los glitches de vcr)","tags":[],"text":"los defectos de lo antiguo son la nostalgia del futuro. (hablando de los errores en ia. por ej, los glitches de vcr)\n","title":""},{"date":"2022-07-25","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/220725_rick-rubin_artist-may-always-maker/","summary":"The artist may not always be the maker. It may be the person who sees the piece and recognize the art in it.","tags":[],"text":"the artist may not always be the maker. it may be the person who sees the piece and recognize the art in it.\n","title":""},{"date":"2021-07-19","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/210719_oca%C3%B1a_palante/","summary":"Pero yo palante. Palante vamoh, terriblemente palante.","tags":[],"text":"pero yo palante. palante vamoh, terriblemente palante.\n","title":""},{"date":"2018-12-26","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/181226_samuel-johnson_uno-ve-perro-caminar/","summary":"Si uno ve a un perro caminar sobre las patas traseras, lo importante no es si lo hace bien o mal, sino simplemente que lo hace","tags":[],"text":"si uno ve a un perro caminar sobre las patas traseras, lo importante no es si lo hace bien o mal, sino simplemente que lo hace\n","title":""},{"date":"2018-11-26","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/181126_trevor-noah_said-cant-control-what/","summary":"My mom said \u0026ldquo;You cant control what people do to you, but you can control how you react.\u0026rdquo; So I promised myself \u0026ldquo;Ill never give a racist person the pleasure of seeing my pain.\u0026rdquo;","tags":[],"text":"my mom said \u0026ldquo;you cant control what people do to you, but you can control how you react.\u0026rdquo; so i promised myself \u0026ldquo;ill never give a racist person the pleasure of seeing my pain.\u0026rdquo;\n","title":""},{"date":"2015-02-03","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/150203_julio-verne_nothing-surprises-an-american/","summary":"Nada puede asombrar a un norteamericano.","tags":[],"text":"nada puede asombrar a un norteamericano.\n","title":""},{"date":"2026-03-13","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/260313_philip-k.dick_pa%C3%ADs-es-gobernantes/","summary":"Créeme, ningún país es mejor que sus gobernantes.","tags":[],"text":"créeme, ningún país es mejor que sus gobernantes.\n","title":""},{"date":"2026-03-08","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/260308_ed-catmull_creatividad-es-cambio/","summary":"La creatividad consiste precisamente en saber trabajar con el cambio.","tags":[],"text":"la creatividad consiste precisamente en saber trabajar con el cambio.\n","title":""},{"date":"2026-01-23","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/260123_siri-husdvet_vestir-es-invenci%C3%B3n-del/","summary":"Vestir es un acto de la imaginación, una invención del yo, una ficción","tags":[],"text":"vestir es un acto de la imaginación, una invención del yo, una ficción\n","title":""},{"date":"2024-04-12","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/240412_albert-einstein_imaginaci%C3%B3n/","summary":"Soy suficientemente artista como para recurrir con libertad a mi imaginación. La imaginación es más importante que el conocimiento. El conocimiento es limitado, la imaginación rodea al mundo.","tags":[],"text":"soy suficientemente artista como para recurrir con libertad a mi imaginación. la imaginación es más importante que el conocimiento. el conocimiento es limitado, la imaginación rodea al mundo.\n","title":""},{"date":"2024-04-12","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/240412_bill-murray_call-in-sick-anyway/","summary":"No sé donde vas, pero, puedes llamar y decir que estás enfermo?","tags":[],"text":"no sé donde vas, pero, puedes llamar y decir que estás enfermo?\n","title":""},{"date":"2022-01-21","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/220121_nick-cave_imagination-awaits-spiritual-ignition/","summary":"Your imagination… is mostly an accidental dance between collected memory and influence… a construction that awaits spiritual ignition.","tags":[],"text":"your imagination… is mostly an accidental dance between collected memory and influence… a construction that awaits spiritual ignition.\n","title":""},{"date":"2021-12-21","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/211221_walter-gropius_know-only-technical-means/","summary":"We know that only the technical means of artistic achievement can be taught, not art itself. The function of art has in the past been given a formal importance which has severed it from our daily life; but art is always present when a people lives sincerely and healthily.\u0026ldquo;Our job is therefore to invent a new system of education that may lead - by way of a new kind of specialized teaching of science and technology - to a complete knowledge of human needs and a universal awareness of them. Thus our task is to make a new kind of artist, a creator capable of understanding every kind of need: not because he is a prodigy, but because he knows how to approach human needs according to a precise method. We wish to make him conscious of his creative power, not scared of new facts, and independent of formulas in his own work.","tags":[],"text":"we know that only the technical means of artistic achievement can be taught, not art itself. the function of art has in the past been given a formal importance which has severed it from our daily life; but art is always present when a people lives sincerely and healthily.\u0026ldquo;our job is therefore to invent a new system of education that may lead - by way of a new kind of specialized teaching of science and technology - to a complete knowledge of human needs and a universal awareness of them. thus our task is to make a new kind of artist, a creator capable of understanding every kind of need: not because he is a prodigy, but because he knows how to approach human needs according to a precise method. we wish to make him conscious of his creative power, not scared of new facts, and independent of formulas in his own work.\n","title":""},{"date":"2021-05-23","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/210523_paul-auster_enfrentarse-a-problemas/","summary":"Lo que importa no es la habilidad para evitar los problemas, sino la manera en que se enfrenta uno a ellos cuando se presentan.","tags":[],"text":"lo que importa no es la habilidad para evitar los problemas, sino la manera en que se enfrenta uno a ellos cuando se presentan.\n","title":""},{"date":"2019-11-08","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/191108_margarita-salas_importante-tener-arrugas-cerebro/","summary":"Lo importante es no tener arrugas en el cerebro.","tags":[],"text":"lo importante es no tener arrugas en el cerebro.\n","title":""},{"date":"2019-05-26","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/190526_voltaire_trabajo-aleja-tres-grandes/","summary":"El trabajo aleja de nosotros tres grandes males: el aburrimiento, el vicio y la necesidad.","tags":[],"text":"el trabajo aleja de nosotros tres grandes males: el aburrimiento, el vicio y la necesidad.\n","title":""},{"date":"2025-12-14","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/251214_lacan_verdad-es-ficci%C3%B3n/","summary":"La verdad tiene estructura de guión.","tags":[],"text":"la verdad tiene estructura de guión.\n","title":""},{"date":"2025-11-27","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/251127_tertullian_believe-stupid/","summary":"I believe because it\u0026rsquo;s absurd.","tags":[],"text":"i believe because it\u0026rsquo;s absurd.\n","title":""},{"date":"2025-05-19","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/250519_ursula-k.-le-guin_art-to-scape-routine/","summary":"The daily routine of most adults is so heavy and artificial that we are closed off to much of the world. We have to do this in order to get our work done. I think one purpose of art is to get us out of those routines. When we hear music or poetry or stories, the world opens up again. We\u0026rsquo;re drawn in - or out - and the windows of our perception are cleansed, as William Blake said. The same thing can happen when we\u0026rsquo;re around young children or adults who have unlearned those habits of shutting the world out.","tags":[],"text":"the daily routine of most adults is so heavy and artificial that we are closed off to much of the world. we have to do this in order to get our work done. i think one purpose of art is to get us out of those routines. when we hear music or poetry or stories, the world opens up again. we\u0026rsquo;re drawn in - or out - and the windows of our perception are cleansed, as william blake said. the same thing can happen when we\u0026rsquo;re around young children or adults who have unlearned those habits of shutting the world out.\n","title":""},{"date":"2021-06-28","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/210628_james-clear_unlearn-previous-ideas/","summary":"Most people don’t want accurate information, they want validating information. Growth requires you to be open to unlearning ideas that previously served you.","tags":[],"text":"most people don’t want accurate information, they want validating information. growth requires you to be open to unlearning ideas that previously served you.\n","title":""},{"date":"2021-06-28","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/210628_thich-nhat-hanh_thich-nhat-hanh-zen/","summary":"To love without knowing how to love wounds the person we love.","tags":[],"text":"to love without knowing how to love wounds the person we love.\n","title":""},{"date":"2019-09-07","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/190907_h.g-wells_nada-perdura-preciso-seguro/","summary":"Nada perdura, nada es preciso y seguro (excepto la mente de un pedante), la perfección es la simple negación de esa inexactitud marginal e ineludible que es la misteriosa e íntimas calidad del Ser.","tags":[],"text":"nada perdura, nada es preciso y seguro (excepto la mente de un pedante), la perfección es la simple negación de esa inexactitud marginal e ineludible que es la misteriosa e íntimas calidad del ser.\n","title":""},{"date":"2019-08-27","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/190827_nancy_tontos-hacen-camas/","summary":"Sólo un tonto haría la cama cada día","tags":[],"text":"sólo un tonto haría la cama cada día\n","title":""},{"date":"2019-02-07","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/190207_dorothy-parker_fucking-busy/","summary":"I am too fucking busy, and vice versa.","tags":[],"text":"i am too fucking busy, and vice versa.\n","title":""},{"date":"2018-10-23","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/181023_doctora-oakley_genios-sobre-ram%C3%B3n-y/","summary":"Cajal dijo algo que a mí me parece muy importante. Le preguntaron: “¿Cómo lo ha hecho? ¿Cómo ha logrado tener tanto éxito?”. Y él dijo: “Yo no soy ningún genio”. Y no lo era, le resultaba difícil aprender. Dijo: “Fui constante y flexible cuando los datos decían que me equivocaba. Fui capaz de cambiar y reintentarlo desde otra perspectiva”. Dijo: “Yo he conocido y trabajado con muchos genios. Y lo malo que tienen los genios, aquellos que consideramos inteligentes y que aprenden rápido, es que se acostumbran a aprender cosas muy rápidamente y a tener siempre razón. Al menos cuando son jóvenes, cuando las respuestas son más sencillas. Y con el tiempo, cuando se hacen mayores y maduran, pueden tender a… están tan acostumbrados a tener siempre razón que sacan conclusiones precipitadas, toman decisiones rápidas, y cuando se equivocan no pueden cambiar de opinión. En lugar de eso, utilizan su inteligencia para idear distintas maneras de justificar su error”.","tags":[],"text":"cajal dijo algo que a mí me parece muy importante. le preguntaron: “¿cómo lo ha hecho? ¿cómo ha logrado tener tanto éxito?”. y él dijo: “yo no soy ningún genio”. y no lo era, le resultaba difícil aprender. dijo: “fui constante y flexible cuando los datos decían que me equivocaba. fui capaz de cambiar y reintentarlo desde otra perspectiva”. dijo: “yo he conocido y trabajado con muchos genios. y lo malo que tienen los genios, aquellos que consideramos inteligentes y que aprenden rápido, es que se acostumbran a aprender cosas muy rápidamente y a tener siempre razón. al menos cuando son jóvenes, cuando las respuestas son más sencillas. y con el tiempo, cuando se hacen mayores y maduran, pueden tender a… están tan acostumbrados a tener siempre razón que sacan conclusiones precipitadas, toman decisiones rápidas, y cuando se equivocan no pueden cambiar de opinión. en lugar de eso, utilizan su inteligencia para idear distintas maneras de justificar su error”.\n","title":""},{"date":"2018-10-02","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/181002_daniel-sloss_laught-is-not-counter/","summary":"Laughter is not the opposite of sadness. Happiness is the opposite of sadness. Laughter is a reaction. Its free to exist in both. If your way of dealing with sadness is to grieve and to cry and do whatnot, congratulations.","tags":[],"text":"laughter is not the opposite of sadness. happiness is the opposite of sadness. laughter is a reaction. its free to exist in both. if your way of dealing with sadness is to grieve and to cry and do whatnot, congratulations.\n","title":""},{"date":"2017-05-28","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/170528_andr%C3%A9-breton_cerdos-fil%C3%B3sofos/","summary":"Un filósofo a quien yo entienda es un cerdo.","tags":[],"text":"un filósofo a quien yo entienda es un cerdo.\n","title":""},{"date":"2016-09-08","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/160908_karen-blixen_cura-todo-siempre-agua/","summary":"La cura para todo es siempre agua salada: el sudor, las lágrimas o el mar.","tags":[],"text":"la cura para todo es siempre agua salada: el sudor, las lágrimas o el mar.\n","title":""},{"date":"2026-03-13","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/260313_fran-lebowitz_smoking-and-plotting-revenge/","summary":"I have two main activities in life. Smoking and plotting revenge.","tags":[],"text":"i have two main activities in life. smoking and plotting revenge.\n","title":""},{"date":"2026-03-10","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/260310_frank-zappa_el-marco-es-lo/","summary":"Lo más importante del arte es el marco. Si John Cage, por ejemplo, dice “voy a ponerme un micrófono de contacto en la garganta y voy a beber un zumo de zanahoria y eso será mi composición”, entonces se considera que su gluglú es su composición porque lo puso dentro de un marco y así lo advirtió: “Es lo que hay, ahora quiero que esto sea música”. A partir de ahí, ya es cuestión de gusto. Sin el anuncio del marco se trata de un tío que está tragando zumo de zanahoria.","tags":[],"text":"lo más importante del arte es el marco. si john cage, por ejemplo, dice “voy a ponerme un micrófono de contacto en la garganta y voy a beber un zumo de zanahoria y eso será mi composición”, entonces se considera que su gluglú es su composición porque lo puso dentro de un marco y así lo advirtió: “es lo que hay, ahora quiero que esto sea música”. a partir de ahí, ya es cuestión de gusto. sin el anuncio del marco se trata de un tío que está tragando zumo de zanahoria.\n","title":""},{"date":"2022-11-08","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/221108_albert-einstein_hombre-solitario-y-social/","summary":"El hombre es, a la vez y al mismo tiempo, un ser solitario y un ser social","tags":[],"text":"el hombre es, a la vez y al mismo tiempo, un ser solitario y un ser social\n","title":""},{"date":"2020-11-07","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/201107_luis-bu%C3%B1uel_alguna-parte-azar-misterio/","summary":"En alguna parte entre el azar y el misterio se desliza la imaginación, libertad total del hombre.","tags":[],"text":"en alguna parte entre el azar y el misterio se desliza la imaginación, libertad total del hombre.\n","title":""},{"date":"2019-10-14","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/191014_jose-mar%C3%ADa-cruz-novillo_dise%C3%B1ador-lanza-flecha-blanco/","summary":"El diseñador lanza la flecha al blanco (\u0026hellip;) sin embargo, nosotros, los artistas, disparamos la flecha y, en el lugar donde se ha clavado, pintamos un circulito. Acertamos siempre.","tags":[],"text":"el diseñador lanza la flecha al blanco (\u0026hellip;) sin embargo, nosotros, los artistas, disparamos la flecha y, en el lugar donde se ha clavado, pintamos un circulito. acertamos siempre.\n","title":""},{"date":"2019-08-11","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/190811_diego-guti%C3%A9rrez_ciencia-e-inventos/","summary":"Hay muchísimos ejemplos que están tan embebidos a la sociedad que no nos damos cuenta. El GPS, por ejemplo. Si Einstein no llega a desarrollar la Teoría de la Relatividad no serían tan precisos como lo son. Si Maxwell no se hubiera puesto a pensar en cómo mezclar electricidad y magnetismo no habría televisiones. Pero Maxwell no estaba pensando en televisiones sino en ciencia, en avanzar el conocimiento, y décadas o siglos más tarde surgen inventos. No podemos estar pensando constantemente en aplicaciones al hablar de ciencia. […] Por ejemplo, antes se creía que durante el sueño se fijaban los recuerdos, y ahora parece que su tarea más importante es desconectar, olvidar lo no importante.","tags":[],"text":"hay muchísimos ejemplos que están tan embebidos a la sociedad que no nos damos cuenta. el gps, por ejemplo. si einstein no llega a desarrollar la teoría de la relatividad no serían tan precisos como lo son. si maxwell no se hubiera puesto a pensar en cómo mezclar electricidad y magnetismo no habría televisiones. pero maxwell no estaba pensando en televisiones sino en ciencia, en avanzar el conocimiento, y décadas o siglos más tarde surgen inventos. no podemos estar pensando constantemente en aplicaciones al hablar de ciencia. […] por ejemplo, antes se creía que durante el sueño se fijaban los recuerdos, y ahora parece que su tarea más importante es desconectar, olvidar lo no importante.\n","title":""},{"date":"2019-04-06","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/190406_crist%C3%B3bal-balenciaga_designer-is-architect-and/","summary":"Un buen modisto debe ser: arquitecto para los patrones, escultor para la forma, pintor para los dibujos, músico para la armonía y filósofo para la medida.","tags":[],"text":"un buen modisto debe ser: arquitecto para los patrones, escultor para la forma, pintor para los dibujos, músico para la armonía y filósofo para la medida.\n","title":""},{"date":"2026-03-13","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/260313_quentin-crisp_optimista-coge-el-tel%C3%A9fono/","summary":"Un pesimista es una persona que, si está en el baño, nunca sale para coger el teléfono. Yo era incorregiblemente optimista.","tags":[],"text":"un pesimista es una persona que, si está en el baño, nunca sale para coger el teléfono. yo era incorregiblemente optimista.\n","title":""},{"date":"2021-11-30","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/211130_maxim-gorky_artist-man-who-digest/","summary":"An artist is a man who digest his own subjective impressions and knows how to find a general objective meaning in them, and how to express them in a convincing form.","tags":[],"text":"an artist is a man who digest his own subjective impressions and knows how to find a general objective meaning in them, and how to express them in a convincing form.\n","title":""},{"date":"2021-08-04","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/210804_carl-sagan_science-is-spiritual-source/","summary":"Science is not only compatible with spirituality; it is a profound source of spirituality.","tags":[],"text":"science is not only compatible with spirituality; it is a profound source of spirituality.\n","title":""},{"date":"2021-04-03","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/210403_agent-cooper_brushed-my-teeth/","summary":"But I haven\u0026rsquo;t brushed my teeth yet.","tags":[],"text":"but i haven\u0026rsquo;t brushed my teeth yet.\n","title":""},{"date":"2019-03-16","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/190316_carlos-ra%C3%BAl-villanueva_carlos-ra%C3%BAl-villanueva/","summary":"El arquitecto es un intelectual, por formación y función. Debe ser un técnico, para poder realizar sus sueños de intelectual. Si tales sueños resultan particularmente ricos, vivos y poéticos, quiere decir que a veces puede ser también un artista.","tags":[],"text":"el arquitecto es un intelectual, por formación y función. debe ser un técnico, para poder realizar sus sueños de intelectual. si tales sueños resultan particularmente ricos, vivos y poéticos, quiere decir que a veces puede ser también un artista.\n","title":""},{"date":"2013-12-01","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/131201_fernando-fern%C3%A1n-g%C3%B3mez_amistad-hombre-mujer/","summary":"Yo creo que puede existir perfectamente una amistad entre un hombre y una mujer, siempre que ese hombre no sea yo.","tags":[],"text":"yo creo que puede existir perfectamente una amistad entre un hombre y una mujer, siempre que ese hombre no sea yo.\n","title":""},{"date":"2026-03-13","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/260313_fran-lebowitz_wonderful-fashion-and-cultural/","summary":"It was a very wonderful fashion and cultural event. Unfortunately, there was a fight on the middle. [Muhammad Ali fight]","tags":[],"text":"it was a very wonderful fashion and cultural event. unfortunately, there was a fight on the middle. [muhammad ali fight]\n","title":""},{"date":"2024-04-15","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/240415_sheehan_sheehan-the-cultural-tutor/","summary":"The history of the world — of human civilisation — is revealed by mundane details of daily life.","tags":[],"text":"the history of the world — of human civilisation — is revealed by mundane details of daily life.\n","title":""},{"date":"2024-04-12","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/240412_boris-vian_two-ways-to-desire/","summary":"Estar satisfecho o chochear - dijo Wolf - es lo mismo. Si ya no se desea nada, tanto da chochear. […] Ten en cuenta que hay dos maneras de no desear nada; tener todo lo que se quería o estar desanimado porque no se ha conseguido.","tags":[],"text":"estar satisfecho o chochear - dijo wolf - es lo mismo. si ya no se desea nada, tanto da chochear. […] ten en cuenta que hay dos maneras de no desear nada; tener todo lo que se quería o estar desanimado porque no se ha conseguido.\n","title":""},{"date":"2024-02-03","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/240203_rousseau_man-born-free-everywhere/","summary":"Man is born free, and everywhere he is in chains.","tags":[],"text":"man is born free, and everywhere he is in chains.\n","title":""},{"date":"2023-03-28","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/230328_hannah-gadsby_learn-part-story-focus/","summary":"You learn from the part of the story you focus on.","tags":[],"text":"you learn from the part of the story you focus on.\n","title":""},{"date":"2023-03-25","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/230325_mauro-entrialgo_mauro-entrialgo/","summary":"De los del Habichuelo aprendí, sobre todo, que en los tebeos (y en cualquier asunto creativo) vale hacer de todo. Porque sí, que se supone que todos lo sabemos, pero la cabeza no se te abre hasta que ves resultados prácticos de aplicar esta evidencia.","tags":[],"text":"de los del habichuelo aprendí, sobre todo, que en los tebeos (y en cualquier asunto creativo) vale hacer de todo. porque sí, que se supone que todos lo sabemos, pero la cabeza no se te abre hasta que ves resultados prácticos de aplicar esta evidencia.\n","title":""},{"date":"2023-02-28","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/230228_hugh_i-killed-my-husband/","summary":"It was 1923. And yes, it was in Finland. […] And I remember reading about this one woman who called the police and said “The man in my house is not my husband.” And the police came over and they said, “This is your husband”. And she said “No. This is not my husband. I killed my husband yesterday.”","tags":[],"text":"it was 1923. and yes, it was in finland. […] and i remember reading about this one woman who called the police and said “the man in my house is not my husband.” and the police came over and they said, “this is your husband”. and she said “no. this is not my husband. i killed my husband yesterday.”\n","title":""},{"date":"2023-02-04","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/230204_steve-albini_tr-606-drumatix-was-my/","summary":"When I first got the 606 (Roland TR-606 Drumatix) I carried it around and listened to it like a walkman, and over the course of a day I would gradually build and re-build a rhythm until it was satisfying to listen to on its own.","tags":[],"text":"when i first got the 606 (roland tr-606 drumatix) i carried it around and listened to it like a walkman, and over the course of a day i would gradually build and re-build a rhythm until it was satisfying to listen to on its own.\n","title":""},{"date":"2021-07-30","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/210730_claudio-f.-gonz%C3%A1lez_disruption-boosts-productivity/","summary":"Las innovaciones disruptivas disparan la productividad.","tags":[],"text":"las innovaciones disruptivas disparan la productividad.\n","title":""},{"date":"2020-10-12","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/201012_luc%C3%ADa-mbom%C3%ADo_sueles-sentirte-aquella-parte/","summary":"Sueles sentirte de aquella parte de ti o reducirte a aquella parte de ti que sientes que está siendo más atacada.","tags":[],"text":"sueles sentirte de aquella parte de ti o reducirte a aquella parte de ti que sientes que está siendo más atacada.\n","title":""},{"date":"2019-11-24","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/191124_serjan-burlak_geometry-reveals-data-patterns/","summary":"Geometry is a language that translates numbers into patterns to reveal which data creates flow, bottlenecks, gravity, viscosity, distribution, hierarchy, connection, grouping, reallocation, alignment, cohesion, separation, or a crash.","tags":[],"text":"geometry is a language that translates numbers into patterns to reveal which data creates flow, bottlenecks, gravity, viscosity, distribution, hierarchy, connection, grouping, reallocation, alignment, cohesion, separation, or a crash.\n","title":""},{"date":"2019-04-19","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/190419_violeta_asumir-mediocridad/","summary":"Probablemente seas una persona mediocre y del montón. No gastes tu tiempo en esforzarte en ser especial y gástalo en asumir la realidad. Así, aunque no seas del todo feliz, al menos no serás un desgraciado el resto de tu vida.","tags":[],"text":"probablemente seas una persona mediocre y del montón. no gastes tu tiempo en esforzarte en ser especial y gástalo en asumir la realidad. así, aunque no seas del todo feliz, al menos no serás un desgraciado el resto de tu vida.\n","title":""},{"date":"2019-01-19","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/190119_steven-wright_when-i-die-leaving/","summary":"When I die, I am leaving my body to science fiction.","tags":[],"text":"when i die, i am leaving my body to science fiction.\n","title":""},{"date":"2016-07-02","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/160702_gustave-flaubert_s%C3%A9-regular-ordenado-vida/","summary":"Sé regular y ordenado en tu vida para poder ser violento y original en tu trabajo.","tags":[],"text":"sé regular y ordenado en tu vida para poder ser violento y original en tu trabajo.\n","title":""},{"date":"2014-01-12","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/140112_alfredo_no-quiero-o%C3%ADrte-m%C3%A1s/","summary":"Márchate, no quiero oírte más, sólo quiero oir hablar de tí.","tags":[],"text":"márchate, no quiero oírte más, sólo quiero oir hablar de tí.\n","title":""},{"date":"2026-03-13","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/260313_luc%C3%ADa-mbom%C3%ADo_s%C3%B3lo-negra/","summary":"Me ha pasado que durante mucho tiempo he sido negra. Y ya está. Y luego he entendido que puedes ser muchas más cosas al mismo tiempo.","tags":[],"text":"me ha pasado que durante mucho tiempo he sido negra. y ya está. y luego he entendido que puedes ser muchas más cosas al mismo tiempo.\n","title":""},{"date":"2026-03-13","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/260313_oliver-sacks_creatividad-es-vida-interior/","summary":"La creatividad implica el poder de inventar, de romper con las maneras existentes de ver las cosas, de moverse libremente en el ámbito de la imaginación, de crear y recrear mundos en la propia mente, y al mismo tiempo de controlar todo eso con una mirada interior crítica. La creatividad tiene que ver con la vida interior, con un flujo de ideas nuevas y sentimientos fuertes.","tags":[],"text":"la creatividad implica el poder de inventar, de romper con las maneras existentes de ver las cosas, de moverse libremente en el ámbito de la imaginación, de crear y recrear mundos en la propia mente, y al mismo tiempo de controlar todo eso con una mirada interior crítica. la creatividad tiene que ver con la vida interior, con un flujo de ideas nuevas y sentimientos fuertes.\n","title":""},{"date":"2026-03-08","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/260308_daniel-sloss_hire-someone-to-love/","summary":"A bunch of people who never took time to learn how to be alone, therefore never learned how to love themselves, so you employed someone else to do it.","tags":[],"text":"a bunch of people who never took time to learn how to be alone, therefore never learned how to love themselves, so you employed someone else to do it.\n","title":""},{"date":"2025-05-27","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/250527_pit%C3%A1goras_n%C3%BAmero-es-el-gobernador/","summary":"Lo que gobierna el mundo y las ideas es el número.","tags":[],"text":"lo que gobierna el mundo y las ideas es el número.\n","title":""},{"date":"2024-12-09","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/241209_nieves-concostrina_j%C3%B3venes-que-crecen/","summary":"Es que los jóvenes tenéis cada vez más años.","tags":[],"text":"es que los jóvenes tenéis cada vez más años.\n","title":""},{"date":"2024-02-07","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/240207_proust_travel-through-different-eyes/","summary":"The only true voyage would be not to travel through a hundred different lands with the same pair of eyes, but to see the same land through a hundred different pairs of eyes\u0026quot;.","tags":[],"text":"the only true voyage would be not to travel through a hundred different lands with the same pair of eyes, but to see the same land through a hundred different pairs of eyes\u0026quot;.\n","title":""},{"date":"2024-02-03","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/240203_james-p.-carse_prepare-for-surprises/","summary":"To be prepared against surprise is to be trained. To be prepared for surprise is to be educated.","tags":[],"text":"to be prepared against surprise is to be trained. to be prepared for surprise is to be educated.\n","title":""},{"date":"2020-08-25","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/200825_kierkegaard_truth-always-rests-minority/","summary":"Truth always rests with the minority … because the minority is generally formed by those who really have an opinion, while the strength of a majority is illusory, formed by the gangs who have no opinion.","tags":[],"text":"truth always rests with the minority … because the minority is generally formed by those who really have an opinion, while the strength of a majority is illusory, formed by the gangs who have no opinion.\n","title":""},{"date":"2019-05-03","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/190503_john-dewey_ciencia-expone-significados-arte/","summary":"La ciencia expone significados; el arte los expresa","tags":[],"text":"la ciencia expone significados; el arte los expresa\n","title":""},{"date":"2013-07-02","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/130702_saskia-sassen_powerless-make-history-slowly/","summary":"Quienes no tienen el poder hacen historia de forma lenta","tags":[],"text":"quienes no tienen el poder hacen historia de forma lenta\n","title":""},{"date":"2022-10-25","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/221025_rick-rubin_there-s-thing-bad/","summary":"There’s no such thing as a bad creation. Sometimes the seemingly bad ones have to happen for a good one to come.","tags":[],"text":"there’s no such thing as a bad creation. sometimes the seemingly bad ones have to happen for a good one to come.\n","title":""},{"date":"2022-10-13","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/221013_c%C3%A9sar-astudillo_sobre-el-arte/","summary":"Arte: despierta ciertos estados emocionales (como el miedo o el asco) que solo buscarías voluntariamente dentro de los confines del arte","tags":[],"text":"arte: despierta ciertos estados emocionales (como el miedo o el asco) que solo buscarías voluntariamente dentro de los confines del arte\n","title":""},{"date":"2021-11-07","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/211107_benjamin-franklin_die-at-25-buried/","summary":"Most people die at 25\u0026hellip; we just don\u0026rsquo;t bury them until they are 70.","tags":[],"text":"most people die at 25\u0026hellip; we just don\u0026rsquo;t bury them until they are 70.\n","title":""},{