tanta importancia como realidad y sueño.\n","title":""},{"date":"2014-11-01","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/141101_nick-cave_the-gears-of-the/","summary":"Those moments when the gears of the heart really change.","tags":[],"text":"those moments when the gears of the heart really change.\n","title":""},{"date":"2026-03-13","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/260313_john-berger_publicidad-objectivo-insatisfacci%C3%B3n/","summary":"La pintura al óleo mostraba aquello que su dueño ya estaba disfrutando de entre sus posesiones y su modo de vida. En cambio, el propósito de la publicidad es hacer que el espectador se sienta marginalmente insatisfecho con su modo de vida presente. No con el modo de vida de la sociedad, sino con el suyo dentro de esa sociedad.","tags":[],"text":"la pintura al óleo mostraba aquello que su dueño ya estaba disfrutando de entre sus posesiones y su modo de vida. en cambio, el propósito de la publicidad es hacer que el espectador se sienta marginalmente insatisfecho con su modo de vida presente. no con el modo de vida de la sociedad, sino con el suyo dentro de esa sociedad.\n","title":""},{"date":"2025-03-17","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/250317_ian-mackaye_music-genre-is-bullshit/","summary":"I am not thinking about genre because my genre as I said is music made by people who dont have a choice in the matter.","tags":[],"text":"i am not thinking about genre because my genre as i said is music made by people who dont have a choice in the matter.\n","title":""},{"date":"2024-05-29","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/240529_tom-eastman_current-internet-five-giant/","summary":"[Current internet is] five giant websites filled with screenshots of text from the other four.","tags":[],"text":"[current internet is] five giant websites filled with screenshots of text from the other four.\n","title":""},{"date":"2023-04-02","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/230402_wynton-marsalis_wynton-marsalis/","summary":"Music is always for the listener. But the first listener is the player.","tags":[],"text":"music is always for the listener. but the first listener is the player.\n","title":""},{"date":"2020-08-06","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/200806_miles-monroe_sex-and-death/","summary":" What do you believe in? Sex and death. Two things that come once in a lifetime. But at least after death you are not nauseous. ","tags":[],"text":" what do you believe in? sex and death. two things that come once in a lifetime. but at least after death you are not nauseous. ","title":""},{"date":"2020-01-01","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/200101_abate-sicard_lenguage-de-se%C3%B1as/","summary":"El lenguaje de señas abre las puertas de\u0026hellip; la inteligencia por primera vez.","tags":[],"text":"el lenguaje de señas abre las puertas de\u0026hellip; la inteligencia por primera vez.\n","title":""},{"date":"2018-04-21","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/180421_ra%C3%BAl-cimas_me-gusta-hacer-cosas/","summary":"Me gusta hacer cosas aunque sepa que no soy bueno para eso.","tags":[],"text":"me gusta hacer cosas aunque sepa que no soy bueno para eso.\n","title":""},{"date":"2026-03-10","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/260310_frank-zappa_rembrandt-marr%C3%B3n/","summary":"Rembrandt lograba su “estilo” mezclando un poco de marrón en cada color.","tags":[],"text":"rembrandt lograba su “estilo” mezclando un poco de marrón en cada color.\n","title":""},{"date":"2026-03-09","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/260309_jake_look-close-enought/","summary":"Everything is the same when you look close enough.","tags":[],"text":"everything is the same when you look close enough.\n","title":""},{"date":"2024-05-16","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/240516_steve-albini_no-goals-but-process/","summary":"I’ve lived my whole life without having goals, and I think that’s very valuable, because then I never am in a state of anxiety or dissatisfaction. I never feel I haven’t achieved something. I never feel there is something yet to be accomplished. I feel like goals are quite counterproductive. They give you a target, and until the moment you reach that target, you are stressed and unsatisfied, and at the moment you reach that specific target you are aimless and have lost the lodestar of your existence. I’ve always tried to see everything as a process. I want to do things in a certain way that I can be proud of that is sustainable and is fair and equitable to everybody that I interact with. If I can do that, then that’s a success, and success means that I get to do it again tomorrow.","tags":[],"text":"i’ve lived my whole life without having goals, and i think that’s very valuable, because then i never am in a state of anxiety or dissatisfaction. i never feel i haven’t achieved something. i never feel there is something yet to be accomplished. i feel like goals are quite counterproductive. they give you a target, and until the moment you reach that target, you are stressed and unsatisfied, and at the moment you reach that specific target you are aimless and have lost the lodestar of your existence. i’ve always tried to see everything as a process. i want to do things in a certain way that i can be proud of that is sustainable and is fair and equitable to everybody that i interact with. if i can do that, then that’s a success, and success means that i get to do it again tomorrow.\n","title":""},{"date":"2024-04-12","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/240412_albert-einstein_matem%C3%A1ticas-mienten/","summary":"En la medida en que las proposiciones de las matemáticas dan cuenta de la realidad, no son seguras; y en la medida en que son seguras, no describen la realidad.","tags":[],"text":"en la medida en que las proposiciones de las matemáticas dan cuenta de la realidad, no son seguras; y en la medida en que son seguras, no describen la realidad.\n","title":""},{"date":"2024-04-12","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/240412_bob-pop_clothes-are-an-editorial/","summary":"¿No estoy mono? Me he puesto pañuelo de colorinchis para la foto y las gafas son totales. Visto fuertecito, sí. La ropa es a la vez una forma de enfrentarse al mundo y una barrera de protección frente al mismo. Vestirse es un editorial.","tags":[],"text":"¿no estoy mono? me he puesto pañuelo de colorinchis para la foto y las gafas son totales. visto fuertecito, sí. la ropa es a la vez una forma de enfrentarse al mundo y una barrera de protección frente al mismo. vestirse es un editorial.\n","title":""},{"date":"2024-04-12","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/240412_john-cleese_introvert-exhibitionist/","summary":"You can be a introvert exhibitionist (somebody told him)","tags":[],"text":"you can be a introvert exhibitionist (somebody told him)\n","title":""},{"date":"2021-08-23","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/210823_naval-ravikant_naval-ravikant/","summary":"The hard thing is seeing the truth. To see the truth, you have to get your ego out of the way because your ego doesn’t want to face the truth. The smaller you can make your ego, the less conditioned you can make your reactions, the less desires you can have about the outcome you want, the easier it will be to see the reality.","tags":[],"text":"the hard thing is seeing the truth. to see the truth, you have to get your ego out of the way because your ego doesn’t want to face the truth. the smaller you can make your ego, the less conditioned you can make your reactions, the less desires you can have about the outcome you want, the easier it will be to see the reality.\n","title":""},{"date":"2021-05-23","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/210523_tom-waits_todos-d%C3%ADas-%C3%A1rbol-derecho/","summary":"Todos los días, el árbol derecho le decía al árbol torcido: “Mírame, soy alto y esbelto. Tú estás todo retorcido y encorvado. Nadie quiere mirarte”. Un día llegaron unos leñadores y vieron el árbol derecho y el árbol torcido, y dijeron: “Cortemos sólo los árboles derechos y dejemos el resto”. Los leñadores talaron todos los árboles derechos y los convirtieron en leños, palillos y papel. Pero el árbol torcido sigue allí, creciendo más fuerte y con una forma más extraña cada día. Con el tiempo, Kellesimone y Casey decidieron que era mucho mejor tener un árbol torcido como padre, aunque llevara los pantalones caídos por las rodillas.","tags":[],"text":"todos los días, el árbol derecho le decía al árbol torcido: “mírame, soy alto y esbelto. tú estás todo retorcido y encorvado. nadie quiere mirarte”. un día llegaron unos leñadores y vieron el árbol derecho y el árbol torcido, y dijeron: “cortemos sólo los árboles derechos y dejemos el resto”. los leñadores talaron todos los árboles derechos y los convirtieron en leños, palillos y papel. pero el árbol torcido sigue allí, creciendo más fuerte y con una forma más extraña cada día. con el tiempo, kellesimone y casey decidieron que era mucho mejor tener un árbol torcido como padre, aunque llevara los pantalones caídos por las rodillas.\n","title":""},{"date":"2020-09-26","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/200926_albert-camus_what-is-a-rebel/","summary":"What is a rebel? A man who says no, but whose refusal does not imply a renunciation. He is also a man who says yes, from the moment he makes his first gesture of rebellion.","tags":[],"text":"what is a rebel? a man who says no, but whose refusal does not imply a renunciation. he is also a man who says yes, from the moment he makes his first gesture of rebellion.\n","title":""},{"date":"2019-08-09","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/190809_rick-deckard_love-as-stranger/","summary":"Sometimes, to love someone\u0026hellip; You gotta be a stranger.","tags":[],"text":"sometimes, to love someone\u0026hellip; you gotta be a stranger.\n","title":""},{"date":"2025-12-07","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/251207_fichte_libre-si-todos-son/","summary":"Sólo son libres aquellos que intentan hacer libres a todos los que les rodean.","tags":[],"text":"sólo son libres aquellos que intentan hacer libres a todos los que les rodean.\n","title":""},{"date":"2024-05-10","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/240510_steve-albini_record-culture-to-outlive/","summary":"The recording part is the part that matters to me – that I’m making a document that records a piece of our culture, the life’s work of the musicians that are hiring me, I take that part very seriously. I want the music to outlive all of us.","tags":[],"text":"the recording part is the part that matters to me – that i’m making a document that records a piece of our culture, the life’s work of the musicians that are hiring me, i take that part very seriously. i want the music to outlive all of us.\n","title":""},{"date":"2023-02-14","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/230214_warren-ellis_no-more-postcards-at/","summary":"Drop out of it all. Read books, watch films, listen to music and drama on the radio. The days when it was like your phone could receive lovely postcards from all over the world are gone.","tags":[],"text":"drop out of it all. read books, watch films, listen to music and drama on the radio. the days when it was like your phone could receive lovely postcards from all over the world are gone.\n","title":""},{"date":"2022-07-06","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/220706_daniel-miller_synth-needs-one-key/","summary":"The thing that pissed me off about punk was you had to learn three chords to be in a punk band. If you had a synthesizer, all you had to do was press one key with a finger.","tags":[],"text":"the thing that pissed me off about punk was you had to learn three chords to be in a punk band. if you had a synthesizer, all you had to do was press one key with a finger.\n","title":""},{"date":"2021-06-28","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/210628_rick-sanchez_i-dont-trust-me/","summary":" Rick: I don\u0026rsquo;t trust me. Do you trust you? Morty: Yes..? Rick: Freak ","tags":[],"text":" rick: i don\u0026rsquo;t trust me. do you trust you? morty: yes..? rick: freak ","title":""},{"date":"2019-12-19","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/191219_ryder-caroll_holding-thoughts-like-trying/","summary":"Holding on to thoughts is like trying to catch a fish with your bare hands: They easily slip from your grasp and disappear back into the muddy depths of your mind. Writing things down allows us to capture our thoughts and examine them in the light of day. By externalizing our thoughts, we begin to declutter our minds.","tags":[],"text":"holding on to thoughts is like trying to catch a fish with your bare hands: they easily slip from your grasp and disappear back into the muddy depths of your mind. writing things down allows us to capture our thoughts and examine them in the light of day. by externalizing our thoughts, we begin to declutter our minds.\n","title":""},{"date":"2019-11-26","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/191126_dan-harmon_ego-can-make-people/","summary":"You can be selfishly motivated, thats ego-driven, but thats as good as ego-driven gets is when you go, \u0026ldquo;I want to be the guy who makes people happy\u0026rdquo;.","tags":[],"text":"you can be selfishly motivated, thats ego-driven, but thats as good as ego-driven gets is when you go, \u0026ldquo;i want to be the guy who makes people happy\u0026rdquo;.\