:"2023-02-13","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/230213_david-lynch_routine-to-be-metally/","summary":"[After describing that he eats everyday the same; tomatoes tuna fish, feta cheese and olive oil for lunch. Little pieces of chicken and broccoli and a little soy sauce. Except when he travels.] Habit in a daily routine. And then when there’s some sort of order there, then you’re free to mentally go off any place. You got a safe sort of foundation and a place to spring off from. It’s very important for me. The pure environment, the more fantastic the interior world can be, it seems to me.","tags":[],"text":"[after describing that he eats everyday the same; tomatoes tuna fish, feta cheese and olive oil for lunch. little pieces of chicken and broccoli and a little soy sauce. except when he travels.] habit in a daily routine. and then when there’s some sort of order there, then you’re free to mentally go off any place. you got a safe sort of foundation and a place to spring off from. it’s very important for me. the pure environment, the more fantastic the interior world can be, it seems to me.\n","title":""},{"date":"2020-11-01","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/201101_david-oreilly_art-for-complement-words/","summary":"We cannot properly describe life using language alone so art fills in these gaps in our understanding. [\u0026hellip;] and beyond this we come to find that is very useful at describing things that dont make sense in language.","tags":[],"text":"we cannot properly describe life using language alone so art fills in these gaps in our understanding. [\u0026hellip;] and beyond this we come to find that is very useful at describing things that dont make sense in language.\n","title":""},{"date":"2019-01-27","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/190127_bob-pop_does-habit-make-monk/","summary":"¿El hábito hace al monje? Lo digo por esas pintas que me lleva.","tags":[],"text":"¿el hábito hace al monje? lo digo por esas pintas que me lleva.\n","title":""},{"date":"2016-08-17","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/160817_louis-ck_morir%C3%A1s-cama-hospital-alguien/","summary":"Morirás en una cama de hospital con alguien sentado al lado mirando su móvil.","tags":[],"text":"morirás en una cama de hospital con alguien sentado al lado mirando su móvil.\n","title":""},{"date":"2026-03-13","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/260313_philip-k.dick_dar-vida-al-texto/","summary":"Se introduce uno de los libros en el receptáculo, por ejemplo Moby Dick. Se programa la duración, largo o breve, y se elige la versión: divertida, literal o triste. Después se coloca el indicador de estilo en la posición que corresponda a uno de los grandes artistas clásicos que animará el libro. Dalí, Bacon, Picasso… El aparato está programado para dar vida al texto, en forma de dibujo animado al estilo de una docena de artistas famosos del sistema solar.","tags":[],"text":"se introduce uno de los libros en el receptáculo, por ejemplo moby dick. se programa la duración, largo o breve, y se elige la versión: divertida, literal o triste. después se coloca el indicador de estilo en la posición que corresponda a uno de los grandes artistas clásicos que animará el libro. dalí, bacon, picasso… el aparato está programado para dar vida al texto, en forma de dibujo animado al estilo de una docena de artistas famosos del sistema solar.\n","title":""},{"date":"2026-01-28","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/260128_yi-yi_half-truth/","summary":" Daddy, can we only know half of the truth? What? I dont get it I can only see whats in front, not whats behind. So I can only know half of the truth, right? ","tags":[],"text":" daddy, can we only know half of the truth? what? i dont get it i can only see whats in front, not whats behind. so i can only know half of the truth, right? ","title":""},