","title":""},{"date":"2024-11-25","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/241125_lavinia-greenlaw_lavinia-greenlawthe-vast-extent/","summary":"The most rewarding step in the process of making art might be the moment of conception, which comes before knowing what the work will look like or express. It is a sensation, a visceral excitement and while the work is impossible to describe, it will never again be as perfect or as clear.","tags":[],"text":"the most rewarding step in the process of making art might be the moment of conception, which comes before knowing what the work will look like or express. it is a sensation, a visceral excitement and while the work is impossible to describe, it will never again be as perfect or as clear.\n","title":""},{"date":"2024-08-07","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/240807_emma-goldman_emma-goldman/","summary":"Si el significado de la anarquía ha sido interpretado como el estado de mayor desorden, es porque han enseñado a la gente que sus asuntos están regulados, que ellos son gobernados sabiamente, y que esa autoridad es una necesidad.","tags":[],"text":"si el significado de la anarquía ha sido interpretado como el estado de mayor desorden, es porque han enseñado a la gente que sus asuntos están regulados, que ellos son gobernados sabiamente, y que esa autoridad es una necesidad.\n","title":""},{"date":"2024-04-12","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/240412_ramon-g%C3%B3mez-de-la-serna_ramon-g%C3%B3mez-de-la/","summary":"El ruido del reloj es que os está cavando la fosa.","tags":[],"text":"el ruido del reloj es que os está cavando la fosa.\n","title":""},{"date":"2023-02-21","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/230221_colm-doherty-p%C3%A1draic-s%C3%BAilleabh%C3%A1in_we-all-remember-mozart/","summary":" Yet we all remember the music of the time. Everyone, to a man, knows Mozart\u0026rsquo;s name. Well, I don\u00