 1 Prise Takt. Dann wird die I I Masse sehr reichlich mit Liebe übergossen. Das fertige Gericht schmücke man mit Sträußchen kleiner Aufmerksamkeiten und serviere es täglich mit Heiterkeit und mit einer guten erquickenden Tasse Tee \u0026hellip;\n[ENG]","tags":[],"text":"[de] altes kochrezept für glücklichkeit (old recipe for happiness) man nehme: 12 monate, putze sie ganz sauber von bitterkeit, geiz, pedanterie und angst und zerlege jeden monat in 30 oder 31 teile, so dass der vorrat genau für ein jahr reicht. es wird jeden tag einzeln angerichtet aus: 1 teil arbeit und 2 teilen frohsinn und humor. man füge 3 gehäufte esslöffel optimismus hinzu, 1 teelöffel toleranz, 1 körnchen ironie und 1 prise takt. dann wird die i i masse sehr reichlich mit liebe übergossen. das fertige gericht schmücke man mit sträußchen kleiner aufmerksamkeiten und serviere es täglich mit heiterkeit und mit einer guten erquickenden tasse tee \u0026hellip;\n[eng]\n","title":""},{"date":"2021-12-14","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/211214_lewis-mumford_when-man-ceases-create/","summary":"When man ceases to create","tags":[],"text":"when man ceases to create\n","title":""},{"date":"2020-02-16","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/200216_leonardo-da-vinci_vida-aprovechada-muerte-feliz/","summary":"Al igual que un día bien aprovechado trae un sueño feliz, una vida bien empleada trae una muerte feliz.","tags":[],"text":"al igual que un día bien aprovechado trae un sueño feliz, una vida bien empleada trae una muerte feliz.\n","title":""},{"date":"2019-01-17","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/190117_mingote_mingote/","summary":"[Sobre la siesta] Para que un hombre esté despierto», decía, «debe despertarse dos veces.","tags":[],"text":"[sobre la siesta] para que un hombre esté despierto», decía, «debe despertarse dos veces.\n","title":""},{"date":"2026-03-13","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/260313_frank-zappa_mezclar-marr%C3%B3n/","summary":"Rembrandt lograba su “estilo” mezclando un poco de marrón en cada color.","tags":[],"text":"rembrandt lograba su “estilo” mezclando un poco de marrón en cada color.\n","title":""},{"date":"2026-03-13","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/260313_leonardo-da-vinci_cabalga-muerte/","summary":"Haz que cabalgue sobre la Muerte, porque la Envidia nunca muere.","tags":[],"text":"haz que cabalgue sobre la muerte, porque la envidia nunca muere.\n","title":""},{"date":"2026-03-10","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/260310_frank-zappa_estilo-musical-requiere-indumentaria/","summary":"Ningún cambio de estilo musical puede sobrevivir si no va acompañado de un cambio en la indumentaria. […] Ninguna innovación musical supondrá un éxito relevante si no se involucra del todo las industrias que reciben un beneficio tangencial: la moda y el merchandising.","tags":[],"text":"ningún cambio de estilo musical puede sobrevivir si no va acompañado de un cambio en la indumentaria. […] ninguna innovación musical supondrá un éxito relevante si no se involucra del todo las industrias que reciben un beneficio tangencial: la moda y el merchandising.\n","title":""},{"date":"2026-03-09","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/260309_max-renn_long-live-the-new/","summary":"Death to Videodrome! Long live the new flesh!","tags":[],"text":"death to videodrome! long live the new flesh!\n","title":""},{"date":"2025-12-15","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/251215_arthur-schopenhauer_want-what-you-want/","summary":"A man can do what he wants, but not want what he wants.","tags":[],"text":"a man can do what he wants, but not want what he wants.\n","title":""},{"date":"2025-08-12","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/250812_arthur-schopenhauer_you-cant-will-your/","summary":"A man can do what he wills, but he cannot will what he wills.","tags":[],"text":"a man can do what he wills, but he cannot will what he wills.\n","title":""},{"date":"2025-05-27","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/250527_richard-feynman_nadie-entiende-la-cu%C3%A1ntica/","summary":"Creo que podemos decir que nadie entiende de verdad la mecánica cuántica.","tags":[],"text":"creo que podemos decir que nadie entiende de verdad la mecánica cuántica.\n","title":""},{"date":"2023-04-02","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/230402_brian-eno_future-revolutions-are-unreadable/","summary":"The revolutions of the future will appear in forms we don’t even recognise—in a language we can’t read. We will be looking out for twists on the old themes but not noticing that there are whole new conversations taking place. Just imagine if all the things about which we now get so heated meant nothing to those who follow us—as mysteriously irrelevant as the nuanced distinctions between anarcho-syndicalism and communist anarchism. At least we can hope for that. As the cybernetician Stafford Beer once said to me: “If we can understand our children, we’re all screwed.” So revel in your mystification and read it as a sign of a healthy future. Whatever happens next, it won’t be what you expected. If it is what you expected, it isn’t what’s happening next.","tags":[],"text":"the revolutions of the future will appear in forms we don’t even recognise—in a language we can’t read. we will be looking out for twists on the old themes but not noticing that there are whole new conversations taking place. just imagine if all the things about which we now get so heated meant nothing to those who follow us—as mysteriously irrelevant as the nuanced distinctions between anarcho-syndicalism and communist anarchism. at least we can hope for that. as the cybernetician stafford beer once said to me: “if we can understand our children, we’re all screwed.” so revel in your mystification and read it as a sign of a healthy future. whatever happens next, it won’t be what you expected. if it is what you expected, it isn’t what’s happening next.\n","title":""},{"date":"2022-11-26","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/221126_paul-auster_un-lugar-para-ver/","summary":"La gente dice que tienes que viajar para ver el mundo. A veces pienso que si te quedas en un lugar y mantienes los ojos abiertos, verás casi todo lo que puedes manejar.","tags":[],"text":"la gente dice que tienes que viajar para ver el mundo. a veces pienso que si te quedas en un lugar y mantienes los ojos abiertos, verás casi todo lo que puedes manejar.\n","title":""},{"date":"2022-07-06","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/220706_martha-beck_way-anything-everything/","summary":"The way you do anything is the way you do everything.","tags":[],"text":"the way you do anything is the way you do everything.\n","title":""},{"date":"2021-07-30","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/210730_makio_no-juzgues/","summary":"Las personas que hablan de los gustos de los demás juzgando si son buenos o malos no van conmigo.","tags":[],"text":"las personas que hablan de los gustos de los demás juzgando si son buenos o malos no van conmigo.\n","title":""},{"date":"2019-02-13","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/190213_bobbie-draper_intense-emotion-politics-and/","summary":"War is an inherently unstable interaction of three things: intense emotion, politics and luck.","tags":[],"text":"war is an inherently unstable interaction of three things: intense emotion, politics and luck.\n","title":""},{"date":"2017-11-28","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/171128_frida-khalo_doctor-me-deja-tomar/","summary":"Doctor, si me deja tomar este tequila le prometo no beber en mi funeral.","tags":[],"text":"doctor, si me deja tomar este tequila le prometo 