adness, and if you lose that\u0026hellip;you\u0026rsquo;re nothing. Note, from me to you, don\u0026rsquo;t ever lose that, cause it keeps you alive.","tags":[],"text":"you got to be crazy. its too late to be sane. too late. you\u0026rsquo;ve got to go full-tilt bozo. \u0026lsquo;cause you are only given a little spark of madness, and if you lose that\u0026hellip;you\u0026rsquo;re nothing. note, from me to you, don\u0026rsquo;t ever lose that, cause it keeps you alive.\n","title":""},{"date":"2018-01-28","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/180128_batou_no-culpes-al-espejo/","summary":"Es inútil culpar al espejo si no te gusta lo que ves en él.","tags":[],"text":"es inútil culpar al espejo si no te gusta lo que ves en él.\n","title":""},{"date":"2017-12-31","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/171231_judah-friedlander_think-new-york-city/","summary":"I think the New York City Marathon is racist. Ten thousand white people chasing five Africans.","tags":[],"text":"i think the new york city marathon is racist. ten thousand white people chasing five africans.\n","title":""},{"date":"2016-08-09","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/160809_lynda-barry_key-eternal-happiness-low/","summary":"The key to eternal happiness is low overhead and no debt.","tags":[],"text":"the key to eternal happiness is low overhead and no debt.\n","title":""},{"date":"2026-03-09","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/260309_stanley-crawford_world-has-magic/","summary":"That the world may or may not be without purpose, but it\u0026rsquo;s not totally without some kind of magic.","tags":[],"text":"that the world may or may not be without purpose, but it\u0026rsquo;s not totally without some kind of magic.\n","title":""},{"date":"2024-04-12","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/240412_bill-murray_so-much-water-just/","summary":" Mirando al océano Pacífico, comentó: Madre mía, cuantísima agua. Y eso solo es la superficie. ","tags":[],"text":" mirando al océano pacífico, comentó: madre mía, cuantísima agua. y eso solo es la superficie. ","title":""},{"date":"2024-04-12","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/240412_ramon-g%C3%B3mez-de-la-serna_cup-causes-its-own/","summary":"El que bebe en taza, hay un momento que sufre eclipse de taza.","tags":[],"text":"el que bebe en taza, hay un momento que sufre eclipse de taza.\n","title":""},{"date":"2024-02-03","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/240203_jean-paul-sartre_believe-is-know-you/","summary":"To believe is to know you believe, and to know you believe is not to believe.","tags":[],"text":"to believe is to know you believe, and to know you believe is not to believe.\n","title":""},{"date":"2023-03-28","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/230328_charles-darwin_trust-not-the-memory/","summary":"Trust nothing to the memory;’ for the memory becomes a fickle guardian when one interesting object is succeeded by another still more interesting.”","tags":[],"text":"trust nothing to the memory;’ for the memory becomes a fickle guardian when one interesting object is succeeded by another still more interesting.”\n","title":""},{"date":"2021-08-06","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/210806_donald-knuth_ai-dont-do-what/","summary":"AI has by now succeeded in doing essentially everything that requires ‘thinking’ but has failed to do most of what people and animals do ‘without thinking","tags":[],"text":"ai has by now succeeded in doing essentially everything that requires ‘thinking’ but has failed to do most of what people and animals do ‘without thinking\n","title":""},{"date":"2021-05-23","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/210523_quentin-crisp_viv%C3%ADa-en-el-futuro/","summary":"Hasta cierto punto, aún vivía en el futuro, un hábito que suele asesinar la felicidad. […] La esencia de la felicidad es la absolutez. Se convierte automáticamente en el estado esencial de aquellos que viven plenametne en el presente continuo. No se requiere de ningún esfuerzo para definir o incluso obtener la felicidad, sino una enorme concentración para abandonar todo lo demás.","tags":[],"text":"hasta cierto punto, aún vivía en el futuro, un hábito que suele asesinar la felicidad. […] la esencia de la felicidad es la absolutez. se convierte automáticamente en el estado esencial de aquellos que viven plenametne en el presente continuo. no se requiere de ningún esfuerzo para definir o incluso obtener la felicidad, sino una enorme concentración para abandonar todo lo demás.\n","title":""},{"date":"2020-05-02","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/200502_robert-frost_three-words-can-sum/","summary":"In three words I can sum up everything I\u0026rsquo;ve learned about life. It goes on.","tags":[],"text":"in three words i can sum up everything i\u0026rsquo;ve learned about life. it goes on.\n","title":""},{"date":"2019-05-09","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/190509_leah-chase_cup-of-gumbo/","summary":"Thats the fun thing about today, look how many people you made happy just with a little cup of gumbo.","tags":[],"text":"thats the fun thing about today, look how many people you made happy just with a little cup of gumbo.\n","title":""},{"date":"2013-10-05","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/131005_ramon-g%C3%B3mez-de-la-serna_ambition-doesnt-know-desire/","summary":"Lo peor de la ambición es que no sabe bien lo que quiere.","tags":[],"text":"lo peor de la ambición es que no sabe bien lo que quiere.\n","title":""},{"date":"2026-03-13","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/260313_frank-zappa_marco-es-lo-importante/","summary":"Lo más importante del arte es el marco. Si John Cage, por ejemplo, dice “voy a ponerme un micrófono de contacto en la garganta y voy a beber un zumo de zanahoria y eso será mi composición”, entonces se considera que su gluglú es su composición porque lo puso dentro de un marco y así lo advirtió: “Es lo que hay, ahora quiero que esto sea música”. A partir de ahí, ya es cuestión de gusto. Sin el anuncio del marco se trata de un tío que está tragando zumo de zanahoria.","tags":[],"text":"lo más importante del arte es el marco. si john cage, por ejemplo, dice “voy a ponerme un micrófono de contacto en la garganta y voy a beber un zumo de zanahoria y eso será mi composición”, entonces se considera que su gluglú es su composición porque lo puso dentro de un marco y así lo advirtió: “es lo que hay, ahora quiero que esto sea música”. a partir de ahí, ya es cuestión de gusto. sin el anuncio del marco se trata de un tío que está tragando zumo de zanahoria.\n","title":""},{"date":"2026-03-13","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/260313_hannah-gadsby_laughter-is-honey/","summary":"Laughter is just the honey, the honey that sweetens the bitter medicine.","tags":[],"text":"laughter is just the honey, the honey that sweetens the bitter medicine.\n","title":""},{"date":"2026-03-13","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/260313_philip-k.dick_chew-zi/","summary":"Chew-Zi: Dios promete la vida eterna, nosotros la proporcionamos.","tags":[],"text":"chew-zi: dios promete la vida eterna, nosotros la proporcionamos.\n","title":""},{"date":"2024-07-23","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/240723_enrico-fermi_enrico-fermi/","summary":"Before I came here I was confused about this subject. Having listened to your lecture I am still confused. But on a higher level.","tags":[],"text":"before i came here i was confused about this subject. having listened to your lecture i am still confused. but on a higher level.\n","title":""},{"date":"2024-05-24","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/240524_kevin-kelly_kevin-kelly/","summary":"You are what you do. Not what you say, not what you believe, not how you vote, but what you spend your time on.","tags":[],"text":"you are what you do. not what you say, not what you believe, not how you vote, but what you spend your time on.\n","title":""},{"date":"2024-04-15","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/240415_benavente_benavente/","summary":"Qué, Don Ramón, ordeñando su mala leche? [A Ramón del Valle-Inclán cuando éste se mesaba la barba.]","tags":[],"text":"qué, don ramón, ordeñando su mala leche? [a ramón del valle-inclán cuando éste se mesaba la barba.]\n","title":""},{"date":"2023-05-29","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/230529_narrator_comedy-is-harder-than/","summary":"Dying is easy. It\u0026rsquo;s comedy that’s hard","tags":[],"text":"dying is easy. it\u0026rsquo;s comedy that’s hard\n","title":""},{"date":"2023-04-02","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/230402_austin-kleon_elders-learn-from-youth/","summary":"The curious elder isn’t interested in judging youth, they’re interested in learning from them.","tags":[],"text":"the curious elder isn’t interested in judging youth, they’re interested in learning from them.\n","title":""},{"date":"2021-07-05","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/210705_bruno-munari_tree-is-an-explosion/","summary":"A tree is a slow explosion of seed.","tags":[],"text":"a tree is a slow explosion of seed.\n","title":""},{"date":"2020-11-07","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/201107_john-lasseter_arte-desaf%C3%ADa-tecnolog%C3%ADa-%C3%A9sta/","summary":"El arte desafía a la tecnología y ésta inspira al arte.","tags":[],"text":"el arte desafía a la tecnología y ésta inspira al arte.\n","title":""},{"date":"2020-09-30","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/200930_rodrigo-cort%C3%A9s_quino-adoptaba-cordura-quien/","summary":"Quino adoptaba la cordura de quien no entiende ni juzga, aunque en realidad lo entendiera todo","tags":[],"text":"quino adoptaba la cordura de quien no entiende ni juzga, aunque en realidad lo entendiera todo\n","title":""},{"date":"2013-08-05","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/130805_pablo-sandoval_perro-de-dos-colas/","summary":"Contento como perro de dos colas.","tags":[],"text":"contento como perro de dos colas.\n","title":""},{"date":"2026-03-13","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/260313_philip-k.dick_obliga-a-todos-a/","summary":"Pero ¿no ve lo que está haciendo? Porque cree que todos están contra usted, obliga a todos a que lo estén.","tags":[],"text":"pero ¿no ve lo que está haciendo? porque cree que todos están contra usted, obliga a todos a que lo estén.\n","title":""},{"date":"2026-03-13","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/260313_tom-waits_tiempo-es-exponencial/","summary":"El tiempo no es una línea, o una carretera, en la que te vas alejando cada vez más de las cosas -dijo-. Todo es exponencial- Todo lo que experimentas cuando tienes dieciocho años sigue estando contigo.","tags":[],"text":"el tiempo no es una línea, o una carretera, en la que te vas alejando cada vez más de las cosas -dijo-. todo es exponencial- todo lo que experimentas cuando tienes dieciocho años sigue estando contigo.\n","title":""},{"date":"2023-12-01","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/231201_richard-feynman_think-getting-close-intelligent/","summary":"I think we are getting close to intelligent machines but they are showing the necessary weaknesses of intelligence.","tags":[],"text":"i think we are getting close to intelligent machines but they are showing the necessary weaknesses of intelligence.\n","title":""},{"date":"2021-12-16","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/211216_ray-bradbury_first-jump-off-cliff/","summary":"First you jump off the cliff and you build your wings on the way down.","tags":[],"text":"first you jump off the cliff and you build your wings on the way down.\n","title":""},{"date":"2021-12-04","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/211204_naval-ravikant_coffee-happiness-beats-yachts/","summary":"If you can’t be happy with a coffee, you won’t be happy with a yacht.","tags":[],"text":"if you can’t be happy with a coffee, you won’t be happy with a yacht.\n","title":""},{"date":"2021-05-23","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/210523_isaac-asimov_hombre-conozca-propio-futuro/","summary":"Un hombre que conozca su propio futuro puede actuar basándose en ese conocimiento y, por consiguiente, cambiar su futuro","tags":[],"text":"un hombre que conozca su propio futuro puede actuar basándose en ese conocimiento y, por consiguiente, cambiar su futuro\n","title":""},{"date":"2020-11-01","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/201101_jeff-tweedy_im-even-willing-say/","summary":"I\u0026rsquo;m even willing to say the songs you don\u0026rsquo;t know you want to write are better than the ones you\u0026rsquo;re picturing.","tags":[],"text":"i\u0026rsquo;m even willing to say the songs you don\u0026rsquo;t know you want to write are better than the ones you\u0026rsquo;re picturing.\n","title":""},{"date":"2020-02-29","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/200229_freeman-dyson_scientists-only-people-who/","summary":"Scientists are not the only people who play with intellectual toys that suddenly explode and cause the crash of empires. Philosophers, prophets, and poets do it, too. In the long run, the technological means that scientists place in our hands may be less important than the ideological ends to which these means are harnessed. Technology is powerful, but it does not rule the world.","tags":[],"text":"scientists are not the only people who play with intellectual toys that suddenly explode and cause the crash of empires. philosophers, prophets, and poets do it, too. in the long run, the technological means that scientists place in our hands may be less important than the ideological ends to which these means are harnessed. technology is powerful, but it does not rule the world.\n","title":""},{"date":"2019-04-20","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/190420_nathan-myhrvold_world-rewards-specialization-comes/","summary":"The world rewards specialization, but specialization comes at a cost. You learn more and more about less and less until you know everything about nothing.","tags":[],"text":"the world rewards specialization, but specialization comes at a cost. you learn more and more about less and less until you know everything about nothing.\n","title":""},{"date":"2019-01-17","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/190117_rodrigo-cort%C3%A9s_mingote-echarse-siesta/","summary":"Mingote era de echarse la siesta, como los hombres importantes que no saben que lo son","tags":[],"text":"mingote era de echarse la siesta, como los hombres importantes que no saben que lo son\n","title":""},{"date":"2026-03-09","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/260309_jake_nothing-is-memorable/","summary":"Nothing she does is memorable, because she does too much.","tags":[],"text":"nothing she does is memorable, because she does too much.\n","title":""},{"date":"2025-11-16","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/251116_caroline-b%C3%B6hmer_exageradamente-feliz/","summary":"Puedo sacar felicidad hasta del sufrimiento","tags":[],"text":"puedo sacar felicidad hasta del sufrimiento\n","title":""},{"date":"2025-01-04","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/250104_ursula-k.-le-guin_holding-doors-open/","summary":"My job is not to arrive at a final answer and just deliver it. I see my job as holding doors open or opening windows.","tags":[],"text":"my job is not to arrive at a final answer and just deliver it. i see my job as holding doors open or opening windows.\n","title":""},{"date":"2024-05-03","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/240503_peter-wilmot-narrator-chuck-palahniuk_hard-to-forget-pain/","summary":"It\u0026rsquo;s so hard to forget pain, but it\u0026rsquo;s even harder to remember sweetness. We have no scar to show for happiness. We learn so little from peace.","tags":[],"text":"it\u0026rsquo;s so hard to forget pain, but it\u0026rsquo;s even harder to remember sweetness. we have no scar to show for happiness. we learn so little from peace.\n","title":""},{"date":"2023-06-13","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/230613_guillermo-del-toro_talismans-imbue-surroundings-with/","summary":"It’s important in our life to have talismans. Everybody has one or two or three. In my case, I have dozens. You have to imbue things that surround you with power.","tags":[],"text":"it’s important in our life to have talismans. everybody has one or two or three. in my case, i have dozens. you have to imbue things that surround you with power.\n","title":""},{"date":"2022-04-03","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/220403_rodrigo-cort%C3%A9s_realismo--pesimismo/","summary":"El realismo es una fórmula que vitalmente da, como mucho, para el conformismo, más que para el optimismo. El realismo renuncia a la imaginación, acorta sus distancias y no quiere ver más allá de lo que hay, cuando, realmente, lo que hay está siempre más allá. Optar por el realismo es ya una opción pesimista, un dar por supuesto que el mundo es su superficie, que la realidad es lo que vemos.","tags":[],"text":"el realismo es una fórmula que vitalmente da, como mucho, para el conformismo, más que para el optimismo. el realismo renuncia a la imaginación, acorta sus distancias y no quiere ver más allá de lo que hay, cuando, realmente, lo que hay está siempre más allá. optar por el realismo es ya una opción pesimista, un dar por supuesto que el mundo es su superficie, que la realidad es lo que vemos.\n","title":""},{"date":"2020-11-07","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/201107_theodor-adorno_toda-obra-arte-delito/","summary":"Toda obra de arte es un delito rebajado","tags":[],"text":"toda obra de arte es un delito rebajado\n","title":""},{"date":"2019-06-27","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/190627_laura-freixas_quer%C3%ADa-tener-hijos-madre/","summary":"Yo quería tener hijos, pero no quería ser madre, quería ser padre.","tags":[],"text":"yo quería tener hijos, pero no quería ser madre, quería ser padre.\n","title":""},{"date":"2025-11-10","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/251110_ordinary-things_easy-money/","summary":"The real danger of the promise of easy money isn\u0026rsquo;t losing what little you already have. It\u0026rsquo;s losing the will to earn it honestly.","tags":[],"text":"the real danger of the promise of easy money isn\u0026rsquo;t losing what little you already have. it\u0026rsquo;s losing the will to earn it honestly.\n","title":""},{"date":"2025-11-08","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/251108_iris-murdoch_philosophy-clarifies-literature-mystifies/","summary":"The aim of philosophy is to clarify and the aim of literature is to mystify.","tags":[],"text":"the aim of philosophy is to clarify and the aim of literature is to mystify.\n","title":""},{"date":"2024-05-10","image":"","imageAlt":"","link":"http://192.168.178.34:1313/quotes/240510_steve-albini_dumb-allies-mean-wrong/","summary":"If the dumbest person is on your side, you\u0026rsquo;re on the wrong side.","tags":[],"text":"if the dumbest person is on your side, you\u0026rsquo;re on the wrong side.\n","title":""},{"date":"2024-04-1